  <span id="freeText6803315786953108668" style="display:none">"I tell you this: it is more profitable to your soul's health, more worthwhile, more pleasing to God and the hosts of Heaven -yes, more helpful to your friends, natural and spiritual, dead or alive- that you should have this blind outreaching love to God, this secret love pressing upon the cloud of unknowing, that you should have this as your spiritual affection, than that you should contemplate and gaze on the angels and saints in heaven, and hear the happy music of the blessed.<br /><br />Do not be surprised at this. See it once (and by grace you can), get hold of it and feel it, and you will see it always."</span>
