        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer902056850" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4928355029239935102">This is the oldest text on Contemplative Christianity written in English. There are several ancient copies in the British Museum, including three copies on velum. The anonymous author gives an outline for what we now refer to as centering prayer. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


